      "impact": "Four test suites mapping to the main views is the right structure. Consider adding a fifth lightweight spec for session/navigation (testing header inputs, nav links, route transitions). The existing unit test structure (MarketList.test.tsx, MarketDetail.test.tsx, Portfolio.test.tsx) validates this organization."
